dc_title_s: Bike Repair Stations City of Madison, WI 2018
dc_description_s: This data layer represents bike repair stations for the City of Madison, Wisconsin in 2018. Bike stations are equipped with a bike pump and different standard tools to fix small bicycle problems.
dc_creator_sm: City of Madison - Metropolitan Planning Organization (MPO)
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data, please visit: https://data-cityofmadison.opendata.arcgis.com/
